summary.span: 定义可用的访问控制项 (ACE) 类型。

span.span: Defines the available access control entry (ACE) types.

remarks.format: ## Remarks MaxDefinedAceType 是当前定义的最大 ACE 类型。MaxDefinedAceType is the largest currently defined ACE type. 自定义 ACE 类型必须定义为大于 MaxDefinedAceType 值。Custom ACE types must be defined to have values larger than MaxDefinedAceType.
